{"type":null,"faqId":11580,"title":"G730-C00 如何启用屏幕解锁图案？","answer":"<p>\n\t<span><span><span>1.</span><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\"><span>点击<b>设置</b><span>-&gt;</span><b>安全</b><span>-&gt;</span><b>屏幕锁定</b><span>-&gt;</span><b>图案</b>。<span></span></span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span><span><span>2.</span><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\"><span>在“<b>选择您的图案</b>”界面，通过手指在屏幕连续划过几个圆的圆心设定解锁时使用的图形样式，再点击“<b>继续</b>”。<span></span></span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span><span><span>3.</span><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\"><span>再次在屏幕上划过刚才的样式，点击“<b>确认</b>”完成解锁图形的设置。<span></span></span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span><span><span>4.</span><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\"><span>当点电源键或开关机时，手机会默认进入图案解锁界面，在该界面划过刚才的图案样式，进行解锁。<span></span></span></span> \n</p>","faqTypeId":143,"faqType":"系统功能与设置","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"2383","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-System-Settings","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1398502029000,"seriesProductName":"G730-C00","visitedTimes":51,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":3,"times":1,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"G730-C00","avgScore":3.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}